
Overwrites (and disables) lengthNorm in Lucene Similarity
See http://web.archiveorange.com/archive/v/AAfXfa9RqrT9Mjm7yu4e

INSTALL
1) Put this jar in <solr-home>/lib 
2) Add this to your  schema.xml:
<!-- disables fieldLength in Similarity-->
<similarity class="org.apache.lucene.search.NoLengthNormSimilarity"/>